Find value of all the above functions at $x = 2$.

2. Let $f(x) = 3x - 1$ and $g(x) = \sqrt{x}$. Find:
   - $f(g(x))$
   - $g(f(x))$
   - $f(f(x))$
   - $g(g(x))$

and visualize functions in a single Geogebra notebook.

